<bibRefCitation author="Granara de Willink, M. C." box="[627,952,674,698]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7" pagination="1 - 183" refId="ref13406" refString="Granara de Willink, M. C. 1999. Las cochinillas blandas de la Republica Argentina (Homoptera: Coccoidea: Coccidae). Contributions on Entomology, International Associated Publishers, 3: 1 - 183." type="journal article" year="1999">Granara de Willink (1999)</bibRefCitation>
